Can I hit on your friend?

563
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,600
You can choose not to.

564
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:56,480
Alright, cheers!

565
00:29:56,960 --> 00:30:00,960
Let's welcome our new friend. Cheers!

566
00:30:01,480 --> 00:30:02,480
Cheers!

567
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,680
Tid-Bow.

568
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:17,120
I remember that she's your friend.

569
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:20,880
Shit, whose dog did I take home?

570
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:24,760
If the owner finds out, you'll be arrested!

571
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:28,120
What should I do, Chai? Help me come up with something.

572
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:31,040
I don't know. Well, isn't she your friend?

573
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:33,800
Oh, what should I do?

574
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:38,960
Oh, Chai!

575
00:30:41,080 --> 00:30:42,080
Hey!

576
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:45,240
Wait...

577
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:48,160
We didn't get drunk and kill Kreetha, did we?

578
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:50,080
It's not "we."

579
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:51,760
You, alone. I'm not involved.

580
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:53,800
You're the one who killed Kreetha.

581
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:56,720
Wait, this is your room, Chai. It's not my room.

582
00:30:56,720 --> 00:31:00,720
You killed Kreetha. You're a murderer, Chai!

583
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,520
Shit!

584
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,000
This couldn't be.

585
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,000
Kreetha's dead.

586
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,720
Hey!

587
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:13,800
You guys are awake now?

588
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:15,000
Kreetha...

589
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:15,960
Oh.

590
00:31:15,960 --> 00:31:17,720
Oh, you're still alive?

591
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,720
Me?

592
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:21,320
I was just resting.

593
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,400
How did you end up looking like that?

594
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:26,760
Well, it's all on you, Chai!

595
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:28,200
Me?

596
00:31:28,520 --> 00:31:29,520
Yes.

597
00:31:33,840 --> 00:31:35,920
Okay, now, we've run out of alcohol!

598
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:38,400
Yay!

599
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:40,800
So, we're good to go now?

600
00:31:40,800 --> 00:31:42,600
Of course.

601
00:31:42,600 --> 00:31:43,920
The party is over!

602
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:44,640
The end!

603
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,040
Okay.

604
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:47,040
Wait, aren't we gonna wait for Kreetha?

605
00:31:48,600 --> 00:31:50,280
Right, where is he?

606
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:52,840
I'm here with something to eat.

607
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:54,320
Omelette with rice?

608
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:55,440
Huh? One portion?

609
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,360
Are you nuts, Kreetha?

610
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:58,760
One. Two. Three. Four. Five.

611
00:31:58,760 --> 00:32:01,520
C'mon, it's okay.

612
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:04,080
Alright, let's have a bite and then, go home.

613
00:32:04,080 --> 00:32:05,080
I'm still hungry.

614
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:16,840
Chai.

615
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,880
I'm sorry.

616
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:22,600
I'll wipe it off for you.

617
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:26,120
Oh, please stop.

618
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:27,480
It's even messier.

619
00:32:27,480 --> 00:32:30,600
How about you go shower at my place?

620
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:31,080
Mmm.

621
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:32,000
Okay.

622
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,720
Your face is a mess too.

623
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:36,520
So, how about Tid-Bow?

624
00:32:36,520 --> 00:32:37,600
The pretty one here?

625
00:32:37,600 --> 00:32:38,200
Right.

626
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,240
Let's take her too.

627
00:32:39,240 --> 00:32:40,800
Let's go, pretty face.

628
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:41,840
Let's go.

629
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,840
Let's go, pretty face.

630
00:32:44,560 --> 00:32:46,560
How about the couch?

631
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:49,000
Oh, there's a couch.

632
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:51,960
We don't wanna lose that. Take it to my place too.

633
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,960
Let's go.

634
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:03,800
Let's go, Tid-Bow.

635
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:07,720
Let's go, Tid-Bow. Let's go, Tid-Bow.

636
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:08,720
Have some.

637
00:33:10,560 --> 00:33:12,560
I'm off.

638
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:25,120
Kree, I'm sorry.

639
00:33:26,280 --> 00:33:27,280
It's alright.

640
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:33,920
So why haven't you showered?

641
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:37,960
Last night, I was too drunk so I chose to sleep.

642
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:44,040
Oh, so you were here all night?

643
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:45,120
That's right.

644
00:33:45,280 --> 00:33:49,280
Then, you must see us...

645
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:50,680
Yes, I did.

646
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:56,600
That's good.

647
00:33:57,320 --> 00:34:01,320
Kree, tell us about what you saw...

648
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:03,920
Did he lose it to me?

649
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:05,920
Or did I lose it to him?

650
00:34:12,160 --> 00:34:15,080
It’s souvenir time, All-New.

651
00:34:15,080 --> 00:34:17,800
Wait, our airline has souvenirs?

652
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:20,160
Newbies really don’t know anything, huh?

653
00:34:20,160 --> 00:34:23,520
We’ve been selling souvenirs forever.

654
00:34:23,520 --> 00:34:25,320
And a brand-new collection of bags is about to drop.

655
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,400
So I gotta hit our sales target.

656
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:28,880
Bags?

657
00:34:30,160 --> 00:34:33,880
I mean bringing money into the company’s bag.

658
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:35,840
The more we earn, the bigger our year-end bonus.

659
00:34:35,840 --> 00:34:38,360
Isn’t that a good thing? Let’s work together!

660
00:34:38,920 --> 00:34:40,200
You got it!

661
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:42,200
Let me do the announcement.

662
00:34:42,680 --> 00:34:44,000
Attention please.

663
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,680
Ladies and gentlemen lounging and napping around the cabin...

664
00:34:46,680 --> 00:34:48,320
The time has come.

665
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:51,360
Today, Glamorous AIrline...

666
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:53,880
is proud to present...

667
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,880
our official souvenirs!

668
00:35:03,720 --> 00:35:07,120
For those who wish to fly safely today,

669
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:11,080
we highly recommend “Luang Pho No-Worries” from Wat Landing.

670
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:13,400
This amulet was blessed for seven days and nights,

671
00:35:13,400 --> 00:35:15,680
until the monk fell asleep during the ritual.

672
00:35:15,680 --> 00:35:19,040
Guaranteed to survive every flight and land like a charm.

673
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:23,040
It’s a must-have for celebs and influencers...

674
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:27,440
people are scrambling to get their hands on it!

675
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,760
What the heck is this...

676
00:35:33,240 --> 00:35:34,240
You're not good at this.

677
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:36,120
Interested?

678
00:35:36,120 --> 00:35:38,080
It's only 999 Baht.

679
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:41,360
One gray bill and you get change, plus a free five-color talisman!

680
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:45,120
I fly every flight and have never had a single accident.

681
00:35:45,120 --> 00:35:48,600
This one boosts charm and popularity.

682
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,200
Stick it at your door,

683
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:54,200
and you'll only get richer!

684
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,280
I'll take two.

685
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:56,720
Two?

686
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,480
Coming right up!

687
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:03,720
This one's extra special.

688
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:06,040
Only one in 100,000 has it.

689
00:36:06,040 --> 00:36:08,520
You're super lucky!

690
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:09,640
I want one more.

691
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:10,520
I do too.

692
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:11,960
Thank you very much.

693
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,320
Wishing you wealth and blessings.

694
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:15,840
Keep it at home for good luck!

695
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:17,840
Sky, you're really good at selling stuff.

696
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:19,360
Are you in need of money?

697
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:21,360
No, I'm helping the company.

698
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:25,360
This one’s packed with sacred power!

699
00:36:27,720 --> 00:36:29,920
It’s sold out. Can’t believe it.

700
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:31,320
Not yet!

701
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,760
There's more?

702
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,960
Milk! Sour flavor for good healthy tummy!

703
00:36:34,960 --> 00:36:38,120
Probiotic yogurt drink with lactobacillus!

704
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,560
Keeps things moving.

705
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,880
Delicious...

706
00:36:40,880 --> 00:36:44,480
and belly-flattening. Interested?

707
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,480
Shit.

708
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:46,040
Three?

709
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:47,600
Sky must really be in need of money.

710
00:36:47,600 --> 00:36:50,120
400 dollars for 3.

711
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,760
Okay, thank you.

712
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:53,840
2? Of course.

713
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,640
This stuff’s amazing.

714
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:57,640
I’ve been pooping non-stop for three days!

715
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:04,240
Just say it, she lost it to me, right?

716
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:06,000
Or did I lose it to her?

717
00:37:06,000 --> 00:37:09,440
My skills? Honey, I'm second to none.

718
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:12,720
And I'm top-tier, baby. Dragon level. Roaring and soaring.

719
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:19,240
Mmm, from what I saw last night, you two were naked.

720
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,240
And then...

721
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:29,960
you two didn't do anything.

722
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:30,960
What?

723
00:37:33,640 --> 00:37:35,200
I'm gonna tell you what I saw...

724
00:37:35,200 --> 00:37:38,080
You two were naked...

725
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:40,080
and then...

726
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:43,080
Then, what?

727
00:37:43,080 --> 00:37:45,080
Then...

728
00:37:49,600 --> 00:37:51,600
Wow, there you are, babe.

729
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:59,880
Wait, the smell...are you drunk?

730
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:05,560
Calm down, Joe.

731
00:38:05,560 --> 00:38:06,560
Calm.

732
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:09,960
But this kinda turns me on too.

733
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,000
Hey, Chai!

734
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,400
Hey!

735
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,760
You said you'd leave the door open!

736
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:27,480
That's right.

737
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:28,000
Tid-Bow, come here.

738
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,000
The couch is very heavy.

739
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:33,160
Took forever to get it in. Got stuck in the elevator too.

740
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,160
Who are these two?

741
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:37,640
Er...

742
00:38:37,640 --> 00:38:39,840
My collegues.

743
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:42,840
And...

744
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,840
I think they wanted to spend a night and I forgot to mention.

745
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:47,000
Wait.

746
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:53,680
You told me to wait here because we were gonna…you know…

747
00:38:53,680 --> 00:38:57,680
Hey, no worries. Do your thing. I’ll watch. I’m into that.

748
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:01,360
Then I'll...

749
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:03,640
put the couch here.

750
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:05,720
You know what, you guys enjoy, I'm out.

751
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:06,560
What?

752
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:09,160
Well, next time, Joe.

753
00:39:09,160 --> 00:39:10,400
Forget it.

754
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,400
We're done here.

755
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:14,120
What?

756
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,160
What?

757
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:15,920
Why?

758
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,920
Now, we don't get to see anything.

759
00:39:16,920 --> 00:39:17,760
No.

760
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,760
What?

761
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,840
What the hell?

762
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:24,360
Tid-Bow, we won't get to watch anything.

763
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:26,360
Make yourself comfortable.

764
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:32,520
Oh, it's hot in here.

765
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,040
It's really hot.

766
00:39:40,520 --> 00:39:41,520
God, it’s suffocating.

767
00:40:15,160 --> 00:40:16,160
It's boiling in here!

768
00:40:51,720 --> 00:40:54,480
You mean…me and Chai, there was never anything between us, right?

769
00:40:54,480 --> 00:40:58,480
Yeah. Just dragging yourselves back here was exhausting enough.

770
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:02,120
Just thinking about it stresses me out.

771
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:05,560
What for? Stressed because you didn't get with me?

772
00:41:05,560 --> 00:41:05,840
What?

773
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:08,760
Can you actually see a couch here?

774
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,880
I’ve gotta haul it back to the office.

775
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,880
And I still have to pay for the cameras I broke into.

776
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:17,760
Hey, at least those two things, we know where they came from.

777
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:20,480
But this one here? What are we gonna do about her?

778
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:21,440
No worries.

779
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:24,080
I’ll take the dog back myself.

780
00:41:24,080 --> 00:41:26,200
Aw, thanks, Kree.

781
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:28,200
Alright, I’ll head out then. Come on, sweetie.

782
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:33,640
I'm off.

783
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:34,640
Hold up, Tid-Gift!

784
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,560
Help me carry this back to the office!

785
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:40,720
You’re a guy, okay?

786
00:41:41,680 --> 00:41:43,680
I’m a girl. How would I be able to lift that?

787
00:41:47,320 --> 00:41:50,120
Hey! Kreetha!

788
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:51,880
He grabbed the dog first.

789
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:53,920
So it's his plan to leave me with this damn couch.

790
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:56,520
I'll go deal with him first.

791
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:57,520
Bye!

792
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:01,120
Hey! Tid-Gift!

793
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,520
Come back here!

794
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:06,600
Gift! How am I supposed to carry this by myself?

795
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:09,160
There’s gender equality laws now, Tid-Gift!

796
00:42:09,160 --> 00:42:11,160
You and me, we’re equal!

797
00:42:15,520 --> 00:42:16,520
How the hell did we get it here?

798
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:28,120
My leg’s numb. Ouch!

799
00:42:28,120 --> 00:42:30,280
Oh, shit, I can’t feel my leg.

800
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:31,080
I can’t feel my leg!

801
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:33,280
Did a snake bite me? Hey!

802
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,160
Chaba!

803
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:34,640
Hey!

804
00:42:34,640 --> 00:42:35,640
Wake up!

805
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:37,000
Are we…toasting?

806
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:40,080
Toasting what? It’s morning already!

807
00:42:40,080 --> 00:42:44,080
You were sleeping on my leg. Holy shit, I can’t feel it at all.

808
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,120
Ouch.

809
00:42:47,120 --> 00:42:49,560
Why the hell are we lying on the floor?

810
00:42:49,560 --> 00:42:50,240
Right.

811
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:52,960
Did Tid-Gift and our frieds leave already?

812
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:53,960
Guess so.

813
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:57,360
Why didn’t we go home last night?

814
00:42:57,640 --> 00:42:58,640
No clue.

815
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:01,240
Why the hell did Tid-Gift leave us passed out like this?

816
00:43:05,680 --> 00:43:07,680
Did anybody hurt me?

817
00:43:08,760 --> 00:43:09,760
Not me.

818
00:43:09,960 --> 00:43:11,960
What about those people walking past?

819
00:43:13,400 --> 00:43:15,400
And we’re just laying here like this...

820
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,760
This calls for a drink.

821
00:43:18,760 --> 00:43:19,880
Are you singing or what?

822
00:43:19,880 --> 00:43:21,880
No, I was talking to you.

823
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:23,520
Meaning?

824
00:43:24,480 --> 00:43:25,560
We go drink more, of course.

825
00:43:25,560 --> 00:43:28,360
Wait, bars aren’t even open at this hour.

826
00:43:28,360 --> 00:43:30,520
I know a place. Let’s go.

827
00:43:30,520 --> 00:43:32,720
Fine, let’s drink ourselves dead. I’m in.

828
00:43:32,720 --> 00:43:33,960
I'll talk to them. Where’s your bag?

829
00:43:33,960 --> 00:43:35,960
Here. Let’s go!

830
00:43:37,840 --> 00:43:38,840
Let’s keep drinking, baby!

831
00:43:39,200 --> 00:43:40,200
Hell yeah.

832
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:41,280
So fun.

833
00:43:41,280 --> 00:43:42,280
‘Til the break of dawn.

834
00:43:43,080 --> 00:43:44,080
And five more mornings after that!

835
00:43:48,680 --> 00:43:49,680
Thank you very much.

836
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:59,120
Today was a banger!

837
00:43:59,120 --> 00:44:01,120
A banger?

838
00:44:01,960 --> 00:44:05,000
Er...I meant you did a great job. That’s what I meant.

839
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:08,040
Oh! Thank you, Sky.

840
00:44:08,040 --> 00:44:11,720
Right, so now go check that the cabin’s in order.

841
00:44:11,720 --> 00:44:13,400
Pick up any trash, okay?

842
00:44:13,400 --> 00:44:15,600
I’ll go check the overhead compartments.

843
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:17,160
Sure thing.

844
00:44:17,160 --> 00:44:18,960
If you find any trash, toss it.

845
00:44:18,960 --> 00:44:22,040
But if you find valuables…bring them to me.

846
00:44:22,040 --> 00:44:24,760
Valuables?

847
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:27,320
Yeah, you know, cash, jewelry, that kinda stuff.

848
00:44:27,320 --> 00:44:31,320
I’m tight with Lost and Found. I’ll make sure it gets returned.

849
00:44:31,320 --> 00:44:34,600
Oh! Got it, Sky.

850
00:44:34,600 --> 00:44:35,600
You ask a lot of questions.

851
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:38,440
Hey.

852
00:44:39,040 --> 00:44:40,520
Someone forgot his passport.

853
00:44:40,520 --> 00:44:41,520
Then keep it.

854
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:44,760
But you’re friends with Lost and Found, aren’t you?

855
00:44:44,760 --> 00:44:47,120
Yeah, but a passport isn’t worth anything.

856
00:44:47,120 --> 00:44:49,000
But the passenger needs it.

857
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:51,400
Well, if you care so much, you give it back to him.

858
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:52,400
Okay.

859
00:44:54,320 --> 00:44:55,320
Sky!

860
00:44:55,320 --> 00:44:56,320
A wallet?

861
00:44:56,680 --> 00:44:57,360
Where?

862
00:44:57,360 --> 00:44:58,360
A passenger left it here.

863
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,320
There’s an ID card in it.

864
00:45:02,480 --> 00:45:03,480
Ooh, cash!

865
00:45:05,080 --> 00:45:07,080
Alright, take it.

866
00:45:07,520 --> 00:45:09,000
I’ll return it to Lost and Found myself.

867
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:10,880
And the rest?

868
00:45:10,880 --> 00:45:11,880
You keep it.

869
00:45:16,080 --> 00:45:18,080
No one else leave anything behind?

870
00:45:20,920 --> 00:45:21,920
What’s that?

871
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:24,000
Huh? Money?

872
00:45:24,960 --> 00:45:25,960
I’ll hold onto that.

873
00:45:26,680 --> 00:45:28,960
You’re too jumpy, you’ll lose it...

874
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:30,480
and we’ll have a whole mess.

875
00:45:30,480 --> 00:45:31,400
Ah, alright.

876
00:45:31,400 --> 00:45:32,400
Now hurry and return that ID.

877
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:33,960
Oh, okay!

878
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:49,960
I'm getting my bag now.

879
00:45:51,880 --> 00:45:53,880
Don’t forget my share!

880
00:45:55,320 --> 00:45:56,320
Your what now?

881
00:45:56,640 --> 00:45:57,640
Fifty percent.

882
00:45:58,920 --> 00:46:00,480
You want half?

883
00:46:00,480 --> 00:46:02,120
Fifty.

884
00:46:02,120 --> 00:46:02,800
Twenty.

885
00:46:02,800 --> 00:46:03,680
Fifty.

886
00:46:03,680 --> 00:46:04,320
Thirty.

887
00:46:04,320 --> 00:46:05,000
Fifty.

888
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:06,280
Forty.

889
00:46:06,280 --> 00:46:09,280
Or…I got this video.

890
00:46:10,320 --> 00:46:12,320
“Thank you. Wishing you all prosperity and fortune.”

891
00:46:13,720 --> 00:46:16,040
Okay, okay, we did work together, huh?

892
00:46:16,040 --> 00:46:18,960
So fifty-fifty’s only fair, right?

893
00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:21,960
That’s what I thought. Fine, fifty-fifty.

894
00:46:26,520 --> 00:46:27,520
Delete that clip!

895
00:46:27,880 --> 00:46:28,880
You got it.

896
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:31,320
Flying with you is such a breeze, Sky.

897
00:46:33,400 --> 00:46:34,400
You little schemer.

898
00:46:35,360 --> 00:46:36,360
Half of my bag is gone now.

899
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:54,320
Why don't you say cut? My dick hurts now.

900
00:46:55,680 --> 00:46:56,680
Okay, cut!

901
00:47:05,040 --> 00:47:06,040
Are they teasing us?

902
00:47:09,240 --> 00:47:10,240
This is so fun!

903
00:47:16,560 --> 00:47:17,560
Okay, cut!

904
00:47:17,720 --> 00:47:18,720
Oh, that's tiring.

905
00:47:18,800 --> 00:47:19,800
It's more tiring than talking.

906
00:47:21,320 --> 00:47:22,320
Hey!

907
00:47:23,320 --> 00:47:24,280
What are you doing?

908
00:47:24,280 --> 00:47:25,440
There's a mosquito.

909
00:47:25,440 --> 00:47:26,440
Alright.

910
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:28,600
Okay, cut!

911
00:47:28,640 --> 00:47:29,640
Are you hurt?

912
00:47:30,240 --> 00:47:31,280
I thought I heard something.

913
00:47:31,280 --> 00:47:32,280
Was that the bone?

914
00:47:33,120 --> 00:47:34,120
I swear I heard something.

915
00:47:35,480 --> 00:47:36,440
One more time.

916
00:47:36,440 --> 00:47:39,800
Tid-Bow, do you like my shirt?

917
00:47:39,800 --> 00:47:43,800
Alright, I'll take my shirt off and put it on for you.

918
00:47:48,600 --> 00:47:49,600
I'm like a crazy woman.

919
00:47:49,840 --> 00:47:50,840
Really crazy.

920
00:47:51,920 --> 00:47:53,920
It's like I'm going out of my mind.

921
00:47:55,640 --> 00:47:57,640
There must be a song!

922
00:48:03,160 --> 00:48:05,160
Who would sing?

923
00:48:05,160 --> 00:48:06,120
Peck, why don't you sing?

924
00:48:06,120 --> 00:48:08,720
Are you singing or are you playing an instrument?

925
00:48:08,720 --> 00:48:10,640
This is so fun! Why don't you sing?

926
00:48:10,640 --> 00:48:11,640
C'mon.

927
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:13,720
My eyes are blurry...

928
00:48:18,000 --> 00:48:19,680
Today, we have a new HR.

929
00:48:19,680 --> 00:48:20,920
I heard that he's very strict.

930
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:22,080
Be prepared.

931
00:48:22,080 --> 00:48:23,040
Screw you!

932
00:48:23,040 --> 00:48:23,600
Guys, stop it!

933
00:48:23,600 --> 00:48:26,080
This is Mr. Mos, our new HR.

934
00:48:26,080 --> 00:48:28,560
I'm going to evaluate each of you.

935
00:48:28,560 --> 00:48:30,440
I'm going to call you...

936
00:48:30,440 --> 00:48:31,360
one by one.

937
00:48:31,360 --> 00:48:32,280
You're nosey.

938
00:48:32,280 --> 00:48:33,280
Hey!

939
00:48:33,280 --> 00:48:33,960
That's All-New.

940
00:48:33,960 --> 00:48:34,720
That's All-New too.

941
00:48:34,720 --> 00:48:35,720
What the hell?

942
00:48:35,960 --> 00:48:36,920
This is Pete.

943
00:48:36,920 --> 00:48:38,920
He's a master of disguise.

944
00:48:39,960 --> 00:48:43,280
If All-New and Kreetha got that disguise skill for their missions...

945
00:48:43,280 --> 00:48:44,560
they'd totally crush it.

946
00:48:44,560 --> 00:48:45,520
You seriously don't know how to talk nicely, do you?
